speaker: OOOOO
text: Say, Jim, how about going for a few beers after dinner?

speaker: XXXXX
text: You know that is tempting but is really not good for our fitness.

speaker: OOOOO
text: It will help us to relax.

speaker: XXXXX
text: It will just make us fat and act silly.

speaker: OOOOO
text: I don't feel like sitting at home.

speaker: XXXXX
text: I suggest a walk over to the gym where we can play singsong and meet some of our friends.

speaker: OOOOO
text: I hear Mary and Sally often go there to play pingpong.

speaker: OOOOO
text: Perhaps we can make a foursome with them.

speaker: XXXXX
text: If they are willing, we could ask them to go dancing with us.

speaker: XXXXX
text: That is excellent exercise and fun, too.

speaker: XXXXX
text: I can do 30 push-ups a minute.

speaker: XXXXX
text: If you do exercise everyday, you can make it, too.

speaker: OOOOO
text: Can you study with the radio on?

speaker: XXXXX
text: The radio has too many comerials.

speaker: OOOOO
text: but then you have to buy a record player.

speaker: XXXXX
text: I will be all right soon.

speaker: XXXXX
text: I was terrified when I watched them fall from the wire.

speaker: XXXXX
text: I started playing ice hockey in a community league.

speaker: XXXXX
text: So I finally got myself new skates.

speaker: XXXXX
text: You don’t have to be able to skate as fast on defense.

speaker: XXXXX
text: I think we play you guys next week.

speaker: XXXXX
text: Well, I have to go to practice.

speaker: XXXXX
text: I’m looking at my horoscope for this month!

speaker: XXXXX
text: It says that I should take a vacation to someplace exotic, and that I will have a passionate summer fling!

speaker: OOOOO
text: Let me see that... What are horoscopes?

speaker: XXXXX
text: It’s a prediction of your month, based on your zodiac sign.

speaker: XXXXX
text: You have a different sign for the month and date you were born in.

speaker: XXXXX
text: I was born on April 15th, so I’m an Aries.

speaker: XXXXX
text: It says that you will be feeling stress at work, but you could see new, exciting developments in your love life.

speaker: XXXXX
text: Looks like we’ll both have interesting summers!

speaker: OOOOO
text: I don't feel any stress at work, and my love life is practically nonexistent.

speaker: OOOOO
text: This zodiac stuff is all a bunch of nonsense.

speaker: XXXXX
text: No, it’s not, your astrology sign can tell you a lot about your personality.

speaker: XXXXX
text: It says that an Aries is energetic and loves to socialize.

speaker: OOOOO
text: Well, you certainly match those criteria, but they’re so broad they could apply to anyone.

speaker: OOOOO
text: What does it say about me?

speaker: XXXXX
text: A Capricorn is serious-minded and practical.

speaker: XXXXX
text: She likes to do things in conventional ways.

speaker: OOOOO
text: He loves the girl very much.

speaker: OOOOO
text: A girl he met on holiday in Spain, I think.

speaker: XXXXX
text: Have they set a date for the wedding?

speaker: OOOOO
text: I hear you bought a new house in the northern suburbs.

speaker: XXXXX
text: we bought it the same day we came on the market.

speaker: OOOOO
text: What kind of house is it?

speaker: OOOOO
text: I love the roof tiles on Spanish style houses.

speaker: XXXXX
text: A house like this in river side costs double the price.

speaker: OOOOO
text: is it a two bedroom house?

speaker: XXXXX
text: it has three bedrooms and three beds and has a living room with a twelve-foot ceiling.

speaker: OOOOO
text: It’ll be a good investment for you.

speaker: XXXXX
text: when will you buy a house?

speaker: OOOOO
text: Not untill the end of this year, you know, just before my wedding.

speaker: XXXXX
text: Not much, except that my mother-in-law is driving me up the wall.

speaker: XXXXX
text: She loves to nit-pick and criticizes everything that I do.

speaker: XXXXX
text: I can never do anything right when she's around.

speaker: XXXXX
text: Well, last week I invited her over to dinner.

speaker: XXXXX
text: My husband and I had no problem with the food, but if you listened to her, then it would seem like I fed her old meat and rotten vegetables.

speaker: XXXXX
text: There's just nothing can please her.

speaker: OOOOO
text: I know you're a good cook and nothing like that would ever happen.

speaker: XXXXX
text: She also criticizes how we raise the kids.

speaker: OOOOO
text: My mother-in-law used to do the same thing to us.

speaker: OOOOO
text: If it wasn't disciplining them enough, then we were disciplining them too much.

speaker: OOOOO
text: She also complained about the food we fed them, the schools we sent them too, and everything else under the sun.

speaker: OOOOO
text: How are Zina's new programmers working out?

speaker: XXXXX
text: I hate to admit it, but they're good.

speaker: XXXXX
text: The Filipino kid is a genius.

speaker: OOOOO
text: So you'll make the Stars.com deadline, and have us up and running next week?

speaker: XXXXX
text: It'll be close but we'll make it.

speaker: OOOOO
text: After Stars.com starts paying us we won't need Vikam's cash anymore.

speaker: XXXXX
text: And if we don't need them, we won't need Zina, either.

speaker: XXXXX
text: I said it's a lovely day.

speaker: XXXXX
text: Why don't we go for a walk?

speaker: OOOOO
text: Well, I feel a little tired.

speaker: OOOOO
text: Then can you wait a few minutes?

speaker: OOOOO
text: I want to finish writing this letter.

speaker: XXXXX
text: It would be a shame not to take advantage of such lovely weather.

speaker: OOOOO
text: Why don't you go ahead and I'll meet you in the park?

speaker: XXXXX
text: Look for me near the lake.

speaker: OOOOO
text: Thank god you showed up when you did!

speaker: OOOOO
text: Do you think we should call the police?

speaker: XXXXX
text: Don’t worry about it I’ll call my friend and have him take care of it.

speaker: XXXXX
text: I can’t believe he was stalking you all these years.

speaker: OOOOO
text: Well... he said I’m not pregnant.

speaker: OOOOO
text: I’m sorry if I got you all worked up over nothing.

speaker: OOOOO
text: I want you to know that I didn’t do it on purpose...

speaker: XXXXX
text: From the moment I met you, not a day has gone by when I haven’t thought of you.

speaker: XXXXX
text: And now that I’m with you again, I’m... I’m just scared, Veronica.

speaker: XXXXX
text: The closer I get to you, the worse it gets.

speaker: XXXXX
text: The thought of not being with you, I mean, I just can’t handle it!

speaker: XXXXX
text: We were made for each other, Veronica.

speaker: XXXXX
text: You are my everything, my soul mate.

speaker: OOOOO
text: Just hold me... I’ll always be here for you no matter what.

speaker: OOOOO
text: And together we can tackle whatever life throws at us.

speaker: XXXXX
text: I’m so happy to hear that!
